					               			<a href="/cn/article/doi/10.19483/j.cnki.11-4653/n.2024.04.006" class="" target="_blank">有限理性视角下高校网络舆情应对研究</a>
               						</div>
				<div class="article-list-author">
																			 							 <span>
								<a  href="javascript:void(0);" onclick='searchLike("authorNameCn","盛宇阳","");'>
								盛宇阳
								</a>
																</span>
