    	            </font>
					        </div>
	        <div class="article-list-zy morenstyle link-block">
				<b>摘要：</b><br/>
								<span class="hidden_line_show"></span>
	        </div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="article-list" id="5f86ae79-c0d3-4b68-ab70-5098c0c0b1a0">
		<div class="article-list-left"><span></span></div>
		<div class="article-list-right">
			<div class="article-list-title">
				          			<a href="/article/doi/10.19483/j.cnki.11-4653/n.2022.02.001" class="mainColor" target="_blank">数字文明：元宇宙中人的虚拟身份认同与媒介化生存</a>
          					</div>
			<div class="article-list-author">
				                                      	<span>
                       	<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="searchLike('authorNameCn','李康跃')">李康跃</a>,                     </span>
                                      	<span>
                       	<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="searchLike('authorNameCn',' 王雪梅')"> 王雪梅</a>,                     </span>
                                      	<span>
                       	<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="searchLike('authorNameCn',' 闫晓阳')"> 闫晓阳</a>                    </span>
                   			</div>
			<div class="article-list-zy">
				    				<font class="font1">
    					    						<a href="/article/doi/10.19483/j.cnki.11-4653/n.2022.02.001" target="_blank">[摘要]</a>(<span class="colorRed abs-num">425</span>)
    					    				</font>
								    																	    	            <font class="font3">
    		            <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="downloadpdf('5f86ae79-c0d3-4b68-ab70-5098c0c0b1a0');">[PDF 1409
    		            KB]</a>(<span class="colorRed pdf-num">78</span>)
    	            </font>
					        </div>
	        <div class="article-list-zy morenstyle link-block">
				<b>摘要：</b><br/>
								<span class="hidden_line_show">技术与社会的繁荣与“再组织”使“元宇宙”概念破壁而出，人们正以此为基点创造一个划时代的数字文明，即数据、人、关系共同构成的未来世界图景。在元宇宙所营造的媒介环境下，人的自我认同完成了由“符号”到“身份”、 由“视听”到“感知”、由“情景”到“社会”的转化。作为第三媒介时代的代表，元宇宙在完成媒介感知的“反向进化”之余，也导致了人的“生存危机”，因此对人在元宇宙中的沉浸式媒介化生存也需辩证看待。</span>
	        </div>
		</div>
	</div>




        </div>
